    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/BySamGordon/status/2035015631699952026",
      "reply_text": "That's a tough spot for the Warriors. Missing key guys hurts.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T17:25:01.724357+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/LALMuse/status/2035041743649767632",
      "reply_text": "Defense has always been a part of his game, but it's getting more recognition now.",
